# Summary
This documentation page describes Amplitude Data's Google Ads integration, which imports daily ad spend, click, and impression data as "Daily Ad Metrics" events, detailing the setup process, prerequisites (Google Ads Customer ID and optional Manager ID), considerations (daily import frequency, per-ad level data), and common issues (permission requirements, data ingestion problems, and metric discrepancies).

